{"tid":1934734,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳肇始︰不排除禁止非香港居民入境","createTime":"2020-03-20T06:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T13:26:35.000Z","uid":20933,"like":18,"dislike":177,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"f74b0b1a6b1c81f23f65dacc1f2374c7ca878629","tid":1934734,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T06:34:28.000Z","msg":"立法會衞生事務委員會討論政府為應對疫情所採取的工作及措施，會上多名議員要求政府禁止非本港居民入境。其中陳凱欣詢問當局，會否對所有由外地抵港的人進行檢疫，及禁止非香港居民入境。公民黨郭家麒批評，政府不封關是最大敗筆，質問政府何時才願意全面封關。<br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局長陳肇始說，非港人的入境人數一直有下跌，政府會繼續監察，不排除會加強現有的措施及禁止非香港居民入境。<br />\n<br />\n她又承認，衛生署的監測範圍有需要再擴大，會要視乎化驗室能力再推展。陳肇始又指，理解部份人希望政府用酒店作檢疫用途，但認為酒店的感染控制情況，不一定適合做檢疫。"},{"pid":"c69880ec90fa3bd65781ff8bfeaa69956523731c","tid":1934734,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T06:34:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1275218&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1275218%26csid%3D261_341&d=wsLpXOxElywvcqXyO2fdBP3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=34fc93a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1275218&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"3ae255115c354d4b1590e44f216de5261c4f1296","tid":1934734,"uid":162910,"like":102,"dislike":61,"score":41,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T06:38:04.000Z","msg":"禁本土都唔禁內地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a49e7b5a76fb924d1d872797a71ad3430258e34b","tid":1934734,"uid":52656,"like":169,"dislike":0,"score":169,"quote":{"pid":"3ae255115c354d4b1590e44f216de5261c4f1296","tid":1934734,"uid":162910,"like":102,"dislike":61,"score":41,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T06:38:04.000Z","msg":"禁本土都唔禁內地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T06:39:11.000Z","msg":"？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e