等有需要的項目。她又質疑，是否不歡迎在外港人回港。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭強調，應該從嚴控風險的角度出發，故減少提供服務的口岸站，集中力量處理某些關口，並對入境人士問得詳細一些，減低來港人士成功暪報的機會，亦會從源頭控制，減少來港人士的比例。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭又引述港大醫學院院長梁卓偉的說法，指現時要討論的問題不是「封關不封關」，而是如何做才適合。她強調，政府減少六個口岸管制站後，政府會監測、適時處理，呼籲市民要持平一點。"},{"pid":"f4fb70a738d15605506069390a23c444365df38c","tid":1934734,"uid":247892,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3ae255115c354d4b1590e44f216de5261c4f1296","tid":1934734,"uid":162910,"like":102,"dislike":61,"score":41,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T06:38:04.000Z","msg":"禁本土都唔禁內地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T10:37:49.000Z","msg":"你講緊咩?<br />\n唔明"},{"pid":"534362659a23fded9f10ff737a81379277796ef8","tid":1934734,"uid":209390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T10:38:19.000Z","msg":"睇死佢又留幾日逃生門比班喪屍衝閘"},{"pid":"e6d3970a3288fbcab426d1ed1166947e9fda0afd","tid":1934734,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T10:45:54.000Z","msg":"baby kingdom JM: 請唔到新家傭，世界末日喇！"},{"pid":"c768b30df9e7ed2fdd47fbcd55c3e6bf85d977e9","tid":1934734,"uid":132590,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3ae255115c354d4b1590e44f216de5261c4f1296","tid":1934734,"uid":162910,"like":102,"dislike":61,"score":41,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T06:38:04.000Z","msg":"禁本土都唔禁內地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T10:48:26.000Z","msg":"唔識字？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1247224f85e3756fa39953712e94851880d9a0a0","tid":1934734,"uid":60455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3ae255115c354d4b1590e44f216de5261c4f1296","tid":1934734,"uid":162910,"like":102,"dislike":61,"score":41,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T06:38:04.000Z","msg":"禁本土都唔禁內地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T10:49:35.000Z","msg":"港島有錢人特權階級<img src=\"/assets/faces/n